Bord Gas Eireann’s Mullins Gives Up Bonus, Reduces Salary by 15%

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-28T17:28:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/bord-gas-eireann-s-mullins-gives-up-bonus-reduces-salary-by-15-.html
Bord Gais Eireann Chief Executive
Officer John Mullins has told the Irish utility’s board that he
will not take payment of a performance bonus for 2010, 2011 and
2012, the company said in an e-mailed statement today. Mullins
also said he would reduce his salary by 15 percent to 250,000
euros ($359,000) a year, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 